descriptionHTML:
This cool watch face boasts record time with a spinning car wheel. Feel the speed as you accelerate with your smartwatch!

- The wheel spins based on your watch acceleration and spins in opposite directions when you move the watch forward or backward (based on the face of the screen on the smartwatch).
- The time is told in 12 and 24 hour options.
- The date on the watch face is told in numerical MM/DD/YYYY format.
- The battery level for the watch is shown.
- RPMs are recorded based on complete rotations of the wheel on the watch face.

This spinning car wheel watch face supports round and square devices, so no matter what watch you have it will work with your android smartwatch.

When downloading this watch face, be sure you have Android Wear installed. You can find it on the play store. It is required to install this car wheel watch face on to your device.

For all available watch faces, visit http://www.osthoro.com/

Search #osthoro
